<HEADLINE>
<P>
FREEWAY REPAIRS ANNOUNCED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Caltrans advises motorists that it plans the following freeway work in the 
Southeast/Long Beach area this week. Repair locations listed below are keyed to 
the nearest city or cities and are spotted on the map by number. 
</P>
<P>
ARTESIA FREEWAY (91) 
</P>
<P>
1. Bellflower/Cerritos: Eastbound No. 6 lane; Woodruff Avenue to San Gabriel 
River Freeway (605); Wednesday, 8:30 a.m. to 2 p.m.; shoulder repair. 
</P>
<P>
2. Cerritos: Eastbound off-ramp at Bloomfield Avenue; today, 12:30 to 2 p.m.; 
electrical repair. 
</P>
<P>
3. Long Beach: Westbound No. 1 lane and westbound connector to southbound Long 
Beach Freeway (710); Monday, 9:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; bridge repair. 
</P>
<P>
4. Paramount: Eastbound connector to northbound Long Beach Freeway (710) and 
Long Beach Boulevard on-ramp; today, 7 a.m. to noon; bridge repair. 
</P>
<P>
HARBOR FREEWAY (110) 
</P>
<P>
5. San Pedro: Westbound No. 1 lane of the Terminal Island separation; Ferry 
Street to Gaffey Street; Wednesday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
6. San Pedro: Eastbound No. 1 lane of the Terminal Island separation; Ferry 
Street to the northbound off-ramp at Harbor Boulevard; Thursday, 9:30 a.m. to 
2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
LONG BEACH FREEWAY (710) 
</P>
<P>
7. Commerce: Northbound connector to the northbound Santa Ana Freeway (5); 
today, 6:30 a.m. to noon; guardrail repair. 
</P>
<P>
8. Commerce: Northbound No. 3 lane; Triggs Street to Olympic Boulevard and the 
Olympic Boulevard off-ramp; Saturday, 5:30 a.m. to noon; bridge guardrail 
repair. 
</P>
<P>
9. Long Beach: Southbound connector to northbound San Diego Freeway (405); 
today, 7 a.m. to 1 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
10. Long Beach: Southbound connector to the eastbound Artesia Freeway (91); 
today, 8:30 to 10 a.m.; electrical repair. 
</P>
<P>
SAN GABRIEL RIVER FREEWAY (605) 
</P>
<P>
11. Cerritos: Southbound connector to the eastbound Artesia Freeway (91); 
today, 6:30 to 8 a.m.; electrical repair. 
</P>
<P>
12. Downey: Southbound connector to the southbound Santa Ana Freeway (5); 
today, 10:30 a.m. to noon; electrical repair. 
</P>
<P>
SANTA ANA FREEWAY (5) 
</P>
<P>
13. Commerce: Northbound and southbound No. 1 lanes; Long Beach Freeway (710) 
to Indiana Street; today, 6:30 a.m. to noon; guardrail repair. 
</P>
<P>
14. East Los Angeles: Southbound No. 5 lane; Ditman Avenue on-ramp to the 
southbound Long Beach Freeway (710) at Triggs Street, and the Olympic Boulevard 
off-ramp; Thursday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
15. Norwalk: Northbound and southbound No. 1 lanes; Orr &amp; Day Road 
overcrossing to Pioneer Boulevard; today, 5:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; guardrail 
repair. 
</P>
<P>
16. Norwalk: Southbound No. 4 lane; Orr &amp; Day Road to Pioneer Boulevard and 
the Pioneer Boulevard off-ramp; Wednesday, 8:30 a.m. to 1:30 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
WHITTIER BOULEVARD (72) 
</P>
<P>
17. Pico Rivera: Eastbound and westbound alternating lanes at Paramount 
Boulevard; Tuesday, 1:30 to 3 p.m.; stenciling. 
</P>
<P>
18. Pico Rivera: Westbound alternating lanes at Rosemead Boulevard; Tuesday, 
noon to 1 p.m.; stenciling. 
</P>
<P>
TERMINAL ISLAND FREEWAY (103) 
</P>
<P>
19. Long Beach: Northbound No. 1 lane; Commodore Schuyler Heim Bridge; 
Wednesday, 9:30 to 11 a.m.; bridge repair. 
</P>
<P>
20. Long Beach: Northbound all lanes; a detour from Anaheim Street to Pacific 
Coast Highway, including the Anaheim Street on-ramp and Pacific Coast Highway 
off-ramp and on-ramp; Thursday, 8:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; bridge repair. 
</P>
