<HEADLINE>
<P>
BEAUTY PAGEANT DATE SET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BELLFLOWER 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jennifer Snow, Miss Bellflower of 1989-90, will relinquish her crown at the 
1990-91 Miss Bellflower Pageant scheduled Oct. 20. The new Miss Bellflower will 
reign for one year and represent the city at various activities and functions. 
Prospective pageant entrants may register at Bellflower City Hall or call 
804-1424, Ext. 208. 
</P>
