SUMMER BASKET CASES; 
</P>
<P>
ORDER ONE OF THESE BOWL PICNICS AND THE ONLY THING YOU'LL HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT 
IS WHETHER OR NOT YOU'VE REMEMBERED THE CORKSCREW. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Biltmore Hotel, 506 S. Grand Ave., Los Angeles, (213) 624-1011 and ask for room 
service. Style: This classy downtown hotel offers four summertime baskets. 
Orders placed before 10 a.m. are ready for pick-up by 4 p.m. the same day. 
Baskets include: Biltmore Bowl Picnic -- pasta salad, croissant sandwich, Brie, 
fresh fruit, pastry and French roll ($20 per person); The French Picnic -- 
