IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SYRIA; PLO -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SYRIA; ASSAD, 
HAFEZ; MUBARAK, HOSNI; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; ARAB NATIONS; PEACE MOVEMENTS 
</P>
