nephew, Greg Sorensen, a 6-3, 260-pound freshman center. ED COMPEAN / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, At Banning High, Ferragamo guided the Pilots to six 
consecutive L.A. City titles. ; Photo, Ferragamo, who failed to develop a 
recruiting pipeline to Banning, suffered through two humbling seasons at Harbor 
College. Los Angeles Times 
</P>
