<TEXT>
<P>
Perhaps the only thing more sickening than the subject matter of Stumbo's "A 
Tale of a Falling Star" was the author's smug observations and editorializing. 
They have no place in what purports to be serious journalism. 
</P>
<P>
LARRY MATHEWS 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
